:<font size="15">קוה</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
קוה / qâvâh / kaw-vaw'

===Etymology===
A primitive root; 

===Verb===
'''קוה'''

# To [[bind]] together (perhaps by twisting), that is, collect; (figuratively) to expect: - [[gather]] (together), look, patiently, [[tarry]], [[wait]] (for, on, upon).

